snippet: In a deal freeing Jason Kidd from his contract with the Nets so he can coach the Bucks, Milwaukee will provide two future second-round draft picks as compensation.
abstract: Deal freeing Jason Kidd from his coaching contract with Brooklyn Nets so he can coach Milwaukee Bucks includes Milwaukee sending Nets two future second-round draft picks as compensation.
lead_paragraph: In a deal freeing Jason Kidd from his contract with the Nets so he can coach the Bucks, Milwaukee will provide two future second-round draft picks as compensation.

headline.main: Nets Said to Get 2 Picks for Kidd
